rssi
----
Ruby-like simple string interpolation for Node.js

Installation
------------
    npm install rssi
    bower install rssi
    wget http://bit.ly/getrssi -O rssi.js

Usage
-----
    var hello = fmt('hello, #{thing}')

    hello({thing: 'world'})
    // -> hello, world

    hello({thing: 'shawarma'})
    // -> hello, shawarma

    // for prevent caching that enabled by default
    hello = fmt('hello, #{thing}', {noCache: true})

